      "ja": "今日はとても楽しかった！",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I'm a little sad we didn't get the cup!",
      "zh": "但我有點難過我們沒拿到杯賽！",
      "ja": "でもカップを取れなくてちょっと悲しい！",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Leo and Maya!",
      "zh": "謝謝你們，Leo和Maya！",
      "ja": "ありがとう、レオとマヤ！",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Playing with you is the best memory today!",
      "zh": "和你們玩是今天最美好的回憶！",
      "ja": "君たちと遊ぶのが今日の最高の思い出だよ！",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See?",
      "zh": "看到了嗎？",
      "ja": "見て？",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Happy memories are better than any metal!",
      "zh": "快樂的回憶比任何金屬都珍貴！",
      "ja": "楽しい思い出はどんな金属よりも価値がある！",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And that is the true meaning of Family Fun Day!",
      "zh": "這就是家庭歡樂日的真正意義！",
      "ja": "それがファミリーファンデーの本当の意味だよ！",
      "time": "00:04:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you for helping us today!",
      "zh": "謝謝你今天幫助我們！",
      "ja": "今日は助けてくれてありがとう！",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are a wonderful family!",
      "zh": "你們是一個很棒的家庭！",
      "ja": "素晴らしい家族だね！",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are so happy!",
      "zh": "我們非常開心！",
      "ja": "とても嬉しいよ！",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Red has great friends like you!",
      "zh": "紅色有像你們這樣的好朋友！",
      "ja": "レッドには君たちのような素敵な友達がいるね！",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes!",
      "zh": "是的！",
      "ja": "はい！",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We are best friends!",
      "zh": "我們是最好的朋友！",
      "ja": "僕たちは親友だよ！",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look at this place!",
      "zh": "看看這個地方！",
      "ja": "この場所を見て！",
      "time": "00:05:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are at the Grand Gyeongbukum Palace!",
      "zh": "我們在大慶福宮！",
      "ja": "私たちはグランド慶福宮にいるよ！",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love this humble!",
      "zh": "我喜歡這個謙遜！",
      "ja": "この謙虚さが好き！",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So much!",
      "zh": "非常喜歡！",
      "ja": "とても！",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel like a real princess today!",
      "zh": "我今天感覺像個真正的公主！",
      "ja": "今日は本物のプリンセスのように感じる！",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And guess what?",
      "zh": "你猜怎麼著？",
      "ja": "そしてね？",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If you wear Hanbuk, you can get free tickets!",
      "zh": "如果你穿韓服，可以免費拿票！",
      "ja": "韓服を着ると無料チケットがもらえるよ！",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello!",
      "zh": "你好！",
      "ja": "こんにちは！",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Welcome to the Grand Korean Royal Palace!",
      "zh": "歡迎來到大韓皇宮！",
      "ja": "グランド韓国王宮へようこそ！",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's play a game!",
      "zh": "我們來玩個遊戲吧！",
      "ja": "ゲームをしましょう！",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Answer my questions, get three stamps, and win a secret gift!",
      "zh": "回答我的問題，集三個印章，贏得秘密禮物！",
      "ja": "私の質問に答えて、3つのスタンプを集めて、秘密のギフトをゲットしよう！",
      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A secret gift?",
      "zh": "秘密禮物？",
      "ja": "秘密のギフト？",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want to find it right now!",
      "zh": "我現在就想找到它！",
      "ja": "今すぐ見つけたい！",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is a big place, Leo!",
      "zh": "這裡很大，Leo！",
      "ja": "ここは広いよ、レオ！",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's walk slowly and enjoy it!",
      "zh": "我們慢慢走，好好享受！",
      "ja": "ゆっくり歩いて楽しもう！",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No running, okay?",
      "zh": "不要跑，好嗎？",
      "ja": "走らないでね、いい？",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, Daddy!",
      "zh": "好的，爸爸！",
      "ja": "わかった、パパ！",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Team Royal Explorers!",
      "zh": "皇家探險隊！",
      "ja": "ロイヤルエクスプローラーズチーム！",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go!",
      "zh": "我們走吧！",
      "ja": "行こう！",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Listen to that loud drum!",
      "zh": "聽那個大聲的鼓聲！",
      "ja": "あの大きな太鼓の音を聞いて！",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is it?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "それは何？",
      "time": "00:06:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They are the Sumangang, the Royal Guards.",
      "zh": "他們是守門將，皇家衛兵。",
      "ja": "彼らはスマンガン、王宮の衛兵です。",
      "time": "00:06:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They protect the Palace Gate.",
      "zh": "他們守護宮門。",
      "ja": "彼らは宮殿の門を守っています。",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is a very old and important tradition.",
      "zh": "這是一個非常古老且重要的傳統。",
      "ja": "これはとても古くて重要な伝統です。",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This wooden house is a giant!",
      "zh": "這座木屋很巨大！",
      "ja": "この木造の家は巨大だ！",
      "time": "00:06:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look at the colorful paint!",
      "zh": "看看這彩色的油漆！",
      "ja": "カラフルなペンキを見て！",
      "time": "00:06:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It helps protect the wood from bugs!",
      "zh": "它幫助保護木頭不被蟲蛀！",
      "ja": "虫から木を守るのに役立つ！",
      "time": "00:06:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And rain!",
      "zh": "還有雨水！",
      "ja": "そして雨からも！",
      "time": "00:06:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is so pretty!",
      "zh": "它真漂亮！",
      "ja": "とても綺麗だね！",
      "time": "00:06:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like a rainbow umbrella for the house!",
      "zh": "就像房子的彩虹傘！",
      "ja": "家のための虹の傘のようだ！",
      "time": "00:06:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look over there!",
      "zh": "看那邊！",
      "ja": "あっちを見て！",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The first stamp!",
      "zh": "第一個印章！",
      "ja": "最初のスタンプ！",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got it!",
      "zh": "拿到了！",
      "ja": "ゲット！",
      "time": "00:06:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One down, two to go!",
      "zh": "完成一個，還有兩個！",
      "ja": "一つクリア、あと二つ！",
      "time": "00:06:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm!",
      "zh": "嗯！",
      "ja": "うーん！",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Something smells so yummy!",
      "zh": "有東西聞起來好香！",
      "ja": "何か美味しそうな匂いがする！",
      "time": "00:06:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is the Royal Kitchen!",
      "zh": "這是皇家廚房！",
      "ja": "ここは王室のキッチンだ！",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They made twelve healthy dishes!",
      "zh": "他們做了十二道健康菜餚！",
      "ja": "12種類の健康的な料理を作った！",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just for the king!",
      "zh": "專為國王準備！",
      "ja": "王様のためだけに！",
      "time": "00:07:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They only used the best food from the whole country!",
      "zh": "他們只用全國最好的食材！",
      "ja": "国中の最高の食材だけを使っている！",
      "time": "00:07:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Listen to the music!",
      "zh": "聽音樂！",
      "ja": "音楽を聴いて！",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It feels like magic!",
      "zh": "感覺像魔法一樣！",
      "ja": "魔法のように感じる！",
      "time": "00:07:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Stamp number two!",
      "zh": "第二個印章！",
      "ja": "2つ目のスタンプ！",
      "time": "00:07:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are almost done!",
      "zh": "我們快完成了！",
      "ja": "もうすぐ終わるよ！",
      "time": "00:07:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want the secret gift!",
      "zh": "我想要秘密禮物！",
      "ja": "秘密のギフトが欲しい！",
      "time": "00:07:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hurry up, Maya!",
      "zh": "快點，Maya！",
      "ja": "急いで、マヤ！",
      "time": "00:07:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Leo!",
      "zh": "Leo！",
      "ja": "レオ！",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Slow down!",
      "zh": "慢點！",
      "ja": "ゆっくり！",
      "time": "00:07:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The stones are slippery!",
      "zh": "石頭很滑！",
      "ja": "石が滑りやすいよ！",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no!",
      "zh": "喔不！",
      "ja": "ああ！",
      "time": "00:07:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My stamp book!",
      "zh": "我的印章本！",
      "ja": "スタンプ帳が！",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:07:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's ruined!",
      "zh": "它壞了！",
      "ja": "壊れちゃった！",
      "time": "00:07:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I can't get the secret gift!",
      "zh": "現在我拿不到秘密禮物了！",
      "ja": "これで秘密のギフトがもらえない！",
      "time": "00:07:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh Leo, are you hurt?",
      "zh": "喔 Leo，你受傷了嗎？",
      "ja": "おお、レオ、大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:07:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please don't cry!",
      "zh": "請不要哭！",
      "ja": "泣かないで！",
      "time": "00:07:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look, my book is still dry!",
      "zh": "看，我的書還是乾的！",
      "ja": "見て、僕の本はまだ濡れてない！",
      "time": "00:07:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can share it!",
      "zh": "我們可以共用它！",
      "ja": "一緒に使おう！",
      "time": "00:07:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We are a team, right?",
      "zh": "我們是一隊，對吧？",
      "ja": "僕たちはチームだよね？",
      "time": "00:07:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You are the best sister, Maya!",
      "zh": "你是最棒的姐姐，Maya！",
      "ja": "マヤ、君は最高の姉だよ！",
      "time": "00:08:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here we are, young Hoeru, the Royal Pavilion!",
      "zh": "我們到了，年輕的 Hoeru，皇家亭！",
      "ja": "ここが若きホエル、王室のパビリオンだ！",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:08:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is floating on the lake!",
      "zh": "它漂浮在湖上！",
      "ja": "湖の上に浮かんでいる！",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The king invited special guests here!",
      "zh": "國王邀請特別賓客來這裡！",
      "ja": "王様は特別なゲストをここに招待した！",
      "time": "00:08:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For grand parties!",
      "zh": "舉辦盛大派對！",
      "ja": "盛大なパーティーのために！",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And beautiful dances!",
      "zh": "還有美麗的舞蹈！",
      "ja": "そして美しいダンス！",
      "time": "00:08:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look at the water!",
      "zh": "看看水面！",
      "ja": "水を見て！",
      "time": "00:08:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is like a giant, quiet mirror!",
      "zh": "它像一面巨大的安靜鏡子！",
      "ja": "それは巨大で静かな鏡のようだ！",
      "time": "00:08:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is so quiet here!",
      "zh": "這裡好安靜！",
      "ja": "ここはとても静かだ！",
      "time": "00:08:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am glad we walked slowly!",
      "zh": "我很高興我們慢慢走！",
      "ja": "ゆっくり歩いてよかった！",
      "time": "00:08:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The last stamp!",
      "zh": "最後一個印章！",
      "ja": "最後のスタンプ！",
      "time": "00:08:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's do it together, Maya!",
      "zh": "我們一起蓋吧，Maya！",
      "ja": "一緒にやろう、マヤ！",
      "time": "00:08:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One, two, three,",
      "zh": "一、二、三，",
      "ja": "いち、に、さん、",
      "time": "00:08:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "stamp!",
      "zh": "蓋章！",
      "ja": "スタンプ！",
      "time": "00:08:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Congratulations, explorers!",
      "zh": "恭喜你們，探險者們！",
      "ja": "おめでとう、探検者たち！",
      "time": "00:08:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You finished the map!",
      "zh": "你們完成了地圖！",
      "ja": "地図を完成させたね！",
      "time": "00:08:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I saw you sharing your book!",
      "zh": "我看到你們分享了書本！",
      "ja": "君たちが本を共有しているのを見たよ！",
      "time": "00:08:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You have a very kind heart, Maya!",
      "zh": "你有一顆非常善良的心，Maya！",
      "ja": "マヤ、とても優しい心を持っているね！",
      "time": "00:08:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And because today is a special palace anniversary,",
      "zh": "而且今天是宮殿特別的週年紀念，",
      "ja": "そして今日は特別な宮殿の記念日だから、",
      "time": "00:08:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "you win our biggest secret gift!",
      "zh": "你贏得我們最大的秘密禮物！",
      "ja": "君たちは最大の秘密のギフトを獲得した！",
      "time": "00:08:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
